			      <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">47.403-3</ph> Disallowance of expenditures.</title>
		    <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
			      <ol id="d2809e13" class="- topic/ol ">
				        <li class="- topic/li ">
					          <p id="d2823e17" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
                  
						            Agencies shall disallow expenditures for U.S. Government-financed commercial international air transportation on foreign-flag air carriers unless there is attached to the appropriate voucher a memorandum adequately explaining why service by U.S.-flag air carriers was not available, or why it was necessary to use foreign-flag air carriers.</p>
				        </li>
